column5: The is it... the official beginning of the year. Everyone (including resort owners) are getting geared up for the season. I love talking about fishing almost as much as I love fishing itself. Feel free to come down and have a few laughs at the show. January 12th-15th at the Pheasant Run Convention Center in St. Charles, IL It's going to be a great time!
Please post the rest of your schedule. If in Minnesota I may look you up.
I'll be in Minneapolis at the Progressive NW Sportshow in late March.
Leaving Oklahoma in the morning to come up for the show. Will be hanging around the Showalter's booth on Saturday, will come say hello.
Ricky, I'll be in Green Bay next week. I'll also be at the Milwaukee Journal show in March.
Have a safe drive. I'm assuming Eddie will be here, right?
